lead_paragraph: A prosecutor with the European Union's foreign mission in Kosovo said on Monday she would sue the mission, accusing it of victimizing her as a whistleblower after she voiced suspicion of corruption in its highest ranks.

headline.main: Prosecutor at Center of EU Graft Scandal in Kosovo Says to Sue
headline.print_headline: Prosecutor at Center of EU Graft Scandal in Kosovo Says to Sue
